<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
        }
        .error-container {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 150px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #088178;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #088178;
        }
        .home-button {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            background-color: #088178;
            border-color: #088178;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background-color: #066c64;
            border-color: #066c64;
        }
        .custom-border {
            border: 2px solid #088178;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container error-container">
        <div class="text-center custom-border">
            <h1 class="error-code mb-4">404</h1>
            <p class="error-message">Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">It seems you've ventured into uncharted territory. Let's get you back on track!</p>
            <a href="/user/home" class="btn btn-lg home-button text-white">
                <i class="bi bi-house-door-fill me-2"></i>Return to Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>